General.Name: Singular Health Group Ltd
General.Description: Singular Health Group Ltd, a medical technology company, engages in the development and commercialization of volumetric rendering platform (VRP) for the 3D and virtual reality (VR) visualization of anatomy using standard radiological imagery. It offers 3Dicom Viewer, a cross-platform application that allows its users to interact with standard 2D medical images; 3DicomVSP, an end-to-surgical planning platform; Health Academy, a scalable multi-lingual platform that provides templated curriculum aligned lessons; and GeoVR, a cloud platform for use in the mineral resources sector. The company was incorporated in 2017 and is headquartered in Subiaco, Australia.
